>\n最後D南亞人就學識修心養性</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教得幾多個啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比佢地陀鐵唔怕一萬都怕萬一啦</blockquote><br />\n朱將軍又黎偉論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d5be80454518ff22d0941bcdf0af00f64317da","tid":108857,"uid":27660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T22:06:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/vlfegkqi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvlfegkqi&h=3066d44d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>1名印度漢非禮，27歲女被捕。"},{"pid":"01221a284dc1200e36c644c64a75da269ff04a3d","tid":108857,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T22:27:54.000Z","msg":"本港近年涉及南亞裔賊人的罪案備受關注，但事實上，安守本分在港生活的仍佔多數。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22166abe27ab045e6b40304bf36e6cd611d8dce4","tid":108857,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T23:28:51.000Z","msg":"印度毅進仔。劣底。"},{"pid":"7570b10e4f6890d1081269cd6946a4d681f61eaf","tid":108857,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T01:10:23.000Z","msg":"let's recruit more inferiors shall we <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cccb91753f5c57134308508ef778b1bec47d387","tid":108857,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T01:12:45.000Z","msg":"其實點解要屈人用中文？應該剩係識英文都可以做公務員喎。 。。。。。"},{"pid":"b8006eab5b44bb6ba7dcc05fff40d0147de6b953","tid":108857,"uid":39257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T01:18:14.000Z","msg":"年輕人在香港擁有向上流動的機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966fbf2d8691f37f47999197c6bd0bbacf3fa9ab","tid":108857,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re